  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 25865d76ba4b75949ade6b09e249db20, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SystemHintInteractable
  hintTitle: '[ MAIN OBJECTIVE: ESCAPE THE ISLAND ] '
  hintContent: 'The escape boat is currently inoperable. You must locate and retrieve
    three missing components to restore its functionality.


    1. Spark Plug: Secured
    inside the shack''s heavy safe.

    Hint: The combination is tied to the sound
    of the fish pools outside. Listen closely to the water splashes to deduce the
    correct sequence.


    2. Jerry Can: Hidden at the bottom of the dry well in
    the woods.

    Hint: You cannot reach it directly. Locate and open the rusted
    water valves in the area to flood the well, forcing the fuel can to float to
    the surface.


    3. Oar Blade: Locked inside the workbench''s hidden drawer.

    Hint:
    Find the three missing tools (Hammer, Pliers, Wrench) and place them on the table
    slots in the correct sequence.

    Warning: An incorrect sequence will trigger
    a loud mechanical jam, alerting nearby enemies to your location.'
  promptMessage: MAIN OBJECTIVE
